37
00:02:23,420 --> 00:02:25,260
This rare scent

38
00:02:25,940 --> 00:02:27,860
is unforgettable once smelled.

39
00:02:28,900 --> 00:02:30,300
The last time I encountered it

40
00:02:30,660 --> 00:02:32,100
was ten years ago,

41
00:02:32,380 --> 00:02:34,060
in Ye's Mansion's southwest Pavilion.

42
00:02:39,660 --> 00:02:41,500
The night Ye Cheng met his tragic end

43
00:02:41,500 --> 00:02:43,740
was a significant event in Shangjing.

44
00:02:43,740 --> 00:02:45,540
Mr. Bai, I'm sure you must know it.

45
00:02:47,060 --> 00:02:48,500
A witness saw

46
00:02:49,060 --> 00:02:51,460
