47
00:02:51,460 --> 00:02:53,220
leaving a white jade pendant behind

48
00:02:53,500 --> 00:02:55,340
at the scene.

49
00:02:57,780 --> 00:02:59,580
I was traveling elsewhere years ago,

50
00:03:00,060 --> 00:03:01,780
